Question: What is Fat Free Puppy ?

Answer: Its a cut-down version of Puppy Linux, All the hard work was done by Big Bass, a regular user of the Puppy Linux irc channel. 

Question: Why did he do it?

Answer: Lately Puppy Linux has been getting bigger and bigger and a lot of application are overlapped, meaning multiple text editors, sound &amp; video applications, etc. So the this version is basically the bare essentials and all you have to do is run your pet-manager and add the application that you really want and not forced to have. Its all about freedom of choice.
